<li><a href="/wiki/Northwestern_University" title="Northwestern University">Northwestern University</a>, honorary doctorate, 1970</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Harvey_Prize&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Harvey Prize (page does not exist)">Harvey Prize</a>, the <a href="/wiki/Technion" title="Technion" class="mw-redirect">Technion</a> of <a href="/wiki/Haifa" title="Haifa">Haifa</a>, <a href="/wiki/Israel" title="Israel">Israel</a>, 1972</li>
